            "racial": ["Strong wing elbows, when flicked forward function as clubs (like swans) ", "spear tongues (like herons) ", "ability to turn it's head 270 degrees ", "silent wing feathers ", "flightlessness in exchange for powerful legs for running, kicking, or swimming ", "voice mimicry ", "squawk loud enough to deafen enemies (like parrots) ", "Long Lifespan (like parrots) ", "Their more dinosaur with scales ", "Extremely maneuverable neck (like flamingos) ", "Strong stomach (like vultures) ", "Purely carnivorous ", "Purely herbivorous ", "Hate Tabaxi ", "Co-exist with harpies ", "Long Decorative Tail Plumage (Like peacocks) ", "Magnetic Navigation (Like homing pigeons) ", "Telescopic Vision (like hawks or eagles) ", "Very cold resistant (like penguins) ", "Very colourful plumage ", "Very good night vision (like owls) ", "Loses a lot of feathers ", "Has a fear of fire ", "Like to fly while drunk ", "Gets angry if someone kills another bird ", "Likes to hop while walking ", "Despite how acclimated they are to normal society, they can't eat any seeded food without wildly pecking at the table. ", "If they awake at sunrise, they feel the need to crow ", "When they molt, they steal anything they can to make another layer of fake feathers ", "Has a gigantic pouch under it's beak (like a pelican). Can hold tiny objects concealed in the throat but has to spit it up awkwardly to speak. ", "Will lift one leg off the ground to rest it if they're standing in one place for a long time (like flamingos). ", "Males usually have brighter and more colorful feathers while females are normally duller. ", "Have special crest of feathers on their heads that stand on end when they feel angry or threatened. ", "Will use their beak to groom themselves (in Aarakocra society see this as unseemly, like a human picking their nose). ", "Has a large red comb on the top of his head and crowd loudly at the rising sun. (like a rooster.) ", ],
